                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">User saved $72 with annual Framer plan. Wanted to switch after 6 months. Lost prepaid months: $90. Switching cost exceeded savings. Monthly plans cost more but preserve flexibility. Annual is a trap unless you're 100% committed to the platform forever.</p>
